title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 145-3.1 - Consultation on amendments to regulations
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 145-3.1 - Consultation on amendments to regulations

State Regulations

Amendments to this Part shall be recommended to the

Regents by the commissioner after consultation with the president of the Higher

Education Services Corporation. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8
§§
145-3.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
